          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I associate a Zippy Online order with my Birth List?",
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Birth Lists created before October 10, 2024:</strong> To link an order placed at Zippy Online to your Birth List you should contact Customer Support and identify the order number you want to link to your Birth List (Link form).<br/><strong>Birth Lists created after October 10, 2024:</strong> Online orders placed with the email address used to create the Birth List are automatically associated with your Birth List.</p>",
