          "type": "faq_item",
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I recover the Birth List membership of an order that has already been received?",
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Birth Lists created before October 10, 2024:</strong> If you have registered an order with an e-mail address other than the one on the Birth List and without its ID in the promotional field, you can still ask to associate it with your Birth List by contacting Customer Service via the form or chat available on the website. You should indicate the telephone number associated with your Birth List and the number of the order already received.<br/><strong>Birth Lists created after October 10, 2024: </strong>Not applicable because when shopping with another email I can't associate it with the list. </p>",
            "header-aee3dd0e9d98c3490ddf154013b369f6": null,
