          "type": "faq_item",
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I check the accumulated value of my Birth List?",
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Birth Lists created before October 10, 2024:</strong> You can request the list of accumulated purchases via the customer service form or chat available on the website. You must indicate the List ID or telephone number associated with it.<br/><strong>Birth Lists created after October 10, 2024: </strong>You can request the list of accumulated purchases via the customer service form or chat available on the website. You must indicate the email address associated with the List.</p>",
