        "faq_item_ECKgp": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I redeem and use the Birth Lists prize?",
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Birth Lists created before October 10, 2024: </strong>The discount promise can only be requested and redeemed in physical shops. It will be delivered in the form of a discount voucher, Zippy gift card or other equivalent means, excluding the promise of a discount in cash. For the holder of the Birth List to be able to access the discount promise after the List has been closed, they must go to a physical shop accompanied by their ID card. The value of the promised discount can be redeemed up to 6 months after the List's closing date, i.e. 18 months after its opening date. After this period, the List is deleted and the discount pledge cannot be redeemed. The prize can only be used in physical Zippy shops. The value of the discount promise will be valid for 1 (one) year after it is issued.<br/><strong>Birth Lists created after October 10, 2024: </strong>When your list is closed, in order to request the discount promise you must send an email to customer service so that the amount to be discounted can be calculated and you must indicate in which physical shop you wish to collect the discount promise. Subsequently, the holder of the Birth List must go to the identified physical shop accompanied by their ID card. It will be delivered in the form of a discount voucher, Zippy gift card or other equivalent means, excluding the promise of a discount in cash. The value of the discount promise can be redeemed up to 6 months after the List's closing date, i.e. 18 months after its opening date. After this period, the List is deleted and the discount promise cannot be redeemed. The prize can be used in Zippy shops. The value of the discount promise awarded will be valid for 1 (one) year after it is issued.</p>",
            "header-3546a8bb6c0c26be8b9c205dbefa2ad0": null,
            "faq_image_1": null,
