          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I link purchases made in a physical shop to my Birth List?",
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Birth Lists created before October 10, 2024: </strong>The addition of new products to the Birth List can be requested by any person in physical shops at the time of purchase, indicating the telephone number associated with the List or the List ID.<br/><strong>Birth Lists created after October 10, 2024:</strong> The addition of new products to the Birth List can be requested by any person in physical shops at the time of purchase, indicating the telephone number associated with the List.</p>",
