          "settings": {
            "heading": "Reporting Irregularities",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Zeitreel has approved its Whistleblowing Regulations and its Policy for the Prevention of Corruption and Related Offences.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>For further information:</strong></p><p>- Whistleblowing Regulations, click <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2711/7127/files/Whistleblowing_Regulation_eng_Zeitreel_2022.pdf?v=1730983003\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2711/7127/files/Whistleblowing_Regulation_eng_Zeitreel_2022.pdf?v=1730983003\"><strong>here</strong></a>;</p><p>- Policy for the Prevention of Corruption and Related Offences click <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2711/7127/files/Policy_on_Prevention_of_Corruption_eng_zeitreel_2022_fbf07141-fafa-42ef-8143-846b2300e529.pdf?v=1730983001\" title=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2711/7127/files/Policy_on_Prevention_of_Corruption_eng_zeitreel_2022_fbf07141-fafa-42ef-8143-846b2300e529.pdf?v=1730983001\"><strong>here</strong></a>.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>To report irregularities:</strong></p><p>- Whistleblowing: breaches of EU law, based on information obtained in the course of their professional activity, as provided for in the respective Regulation;</p><p>- Prevention of Corruption and Related Offences: crimes of corruption and related offences as provided for in the Policy for the Prevention of Corruption and Offences.</p><p>You can use one of the following channels:</p><p>- Email address: comunicacao.irregularidades@zeitreel.com. </p><p>- Zeitreel's Whistleblowing & Anticorruption Officer: Sonae Maia Business Centre, Edificio 2E, Lugar do Espido - Via Norte, 4470-179 Maia, Portugal.<br/></p><p>Zeitreel has approved its Whistleblowing Regulations and its Policy for the Prevention of Corruption and Related Offences.</p>",
