            "heading": "What are the delivery times?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>[table1]</p><p>*Bulky nursery items will have a fixed cost of â‚¬5.99, advertised on the product page and in your shopping basket.</p><p>**In addition to the times above, there are between 5 and 10 working days for the Azores and between 5 and 7 working days for Madeira. For the islands, deliveries always have a fixed cost of â‚¬5.50.</p>",
