          "settings": {
            "heading": "What are the return conditions?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Returns are always free at Zippy!</p><p>Online orders can only be returned, exchanges are not possible.</p><p>To return your order, you can go to one of our physical stores or schedule home pickup using the <a href=\"https://zippyonline.com/pages/return-request/\">return form.</a></p><p>You have <strong>30 days to return your parcel</strong> from the day it is received at your home or arrives at the intended shop.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_y8gqML": {
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do returns work for online purchases in physical shops?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Online orders can be returned to Zippy stores and no exchanges are possible. </p><p>However, please note that returns are not allowed in Zippy stores (except Zippy Outlet stores) for products purchased in Zippy Outlet stores. </p><p>Refunds are processed centrally to the original means of payment and not in-store. </p><p>Refunds on returns to Zippy Outlet shops are made within 14 days of the date of delivery of the items to the shop and validation of their conformity. Once the return has been processed, you will receive an email with the credit note. </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_tmMD6r": {
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do returns with home collection work?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>If you wish, we will collect your parcel free of charge from the address you want.<br/>You can request home collection using the <a href=\"/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Contact\">contact form</a><strong>, </strong>choosing â€˜Returnâ€™ as the reason.</p><p>Fill in the personal details requested and tell us the number of the parcel you wish to return. You will then receive an e-mail from our Customer Service department confirming the<br/>collection.</p><p>Pick-ups are carried out by<strong> CTT on working days, between 9am and 7pm, </strong>and it is not possible to set a time window.</p><p>Refunds for returns with home pick-up are made within 14 days from the day the items are received at our centre and checked for conformity.</p><p>Refunds via home collection are always made to the original means of payment. As soon as the return is processed, you will receive an e-mail with the credit note.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_yGYgmj": {
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How and when will I receive my refund?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Refunds are always made to the <strong>original means of payment</strong> and processed within <strong>14 days </strong>of receiving the items at the returns centre.</p><p>You will receive an email notification confirming that your order has arrived at our centre, as well as a new notification when it has been returned.</p><p>If the original method of payment was Multibanco, you should allow 1-3 working days for the money to be available in your bank account.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_eQckar": {
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I return an online order to a Zippy shop?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Online orders can be returned to Zippy stores and no exchanges are possible. </p><p>However, please note that returns are not allowed in Zippy stores (except Zippy Outlet stores) for products purchased in Zippy Outlet stores. </p><p>Refunds are processed centrally to the original means of payment and not in-store. </p><p>Refunds on returns to Zippy Outlet shops are made within 14 days of the date of delivery of the items to the shop and validation of their conformity. Once the return has been processed, you will receive an email with the credit note. </p><p>You have 30 days to make the return from the day you receive your order at home or the day it arrives at the desired shop.</p>"
          }
        },
