            "faq_answer": "<p>We have the following payment methods at your disposal:</p><ul><li><strong>Mbway </strong> </li><li><strong>Multibanco </strong></li><li><strong>Visa</strong></li><li><strong>Mastercard</strong></li><li><strong>Paypal</strong></li></ul>",
