      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_EWmxKW": {
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Am I entitled to a birthday gift?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Yes. The birthday special offer consists of a newsletter with a <strong>promotional code for a â‚¬5 </strong>discount on a purchase of â‚¬5 or more in the Zippy online shop, within the time period set for this purpose.<br/>The birthday offer can only be used on a single purchase in the Zippy online shop and cannot be combined with other campaigns in place.<br/>The return/cancellation of the transaction in which this discount was used will result in the amount of the promotional code being returned in the form of a voucher. The voucher will be available to view in the <strong>\"Personal Area\" </strong>and can be used as a means of payment. To take advantage of this offer, you must be a subscriber to Zippy's newsletters and have authorised the sending of communications by e-mail. You must also have up-to-date information on your child(ren)'s date of birth in your <strong>\"Personal Area\"</strong>.<br/>This offer will be available by e-mail 7 days before each child's birthday, up to and including their 12th birthday.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_7ghWcM": {
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I use a promotional code?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>A promotional code is an offer code provided by Zippy. It must be used on the <strong>â€˜Checkout'</strong> and before finalising the purchase, by applying it in the <strong>â€˜Promotional Codeâ€™</strong> field.<br/>The period of use varies from offer to offer and is duly communicated. Pay attention to its expiry date.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_Khcfff": {
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What campaigns are currently running?",
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Mid Season Sale</strong><br/>Up to -50% on selected items in force from 13/05/2025 to 02/06/2025 and limited to existing stock.<br/><br/><br/><strong>\"Emotions Markers\" Offer </strong><br/>When purchasing the \"Emotions Pajamas\" (ref. 31068887041), you are entitled to the \"Emotions Markers\" offer (ref. 31075342035). Bookmarks must be added to the cart and the discount is automatically applied at checkout. Offer valid from 02/19/2025 to 12/31/2025, limited to existing stock.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_wGeAj": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Continente Card, can I use it online?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>In Zippy physical stores you can benefit from all the benefits inherent to Continente Card loyalty:<br/>- Make payments, refund the balance in whole or in part;<br/>- Accumulate points and use the coupons issued by this brand.<br/><br/>See all the information, offers and benefits in the General Conditions of the Continente Card here.<br/><br/>It will not be possible to use the Continente Card in the online store.</p>",
