        "faq_item_meDM7C": {
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What care should I take with my clothes?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>We advise you to check the information available on the product pages regarding composition and washing care. However, we do have a few recommendations for maintaining the integrity of your items:Â <br/>- When washing your clothes, you should separate them into different colours and, depending on how dirty they are, avoid exposing them to longer cycles than necessary;Â <br/>- Washing at high temperatures damages the integrity of fabrics and makes colours less vibrant, so try to wash at low temperatures;<br/>- Exposure to direct sunlight causes colours to wear out, so try to dry them in environments that are protected from sunlight;<br/>- Detergent is a cleaning agent, but it can also cause abrasion to fabrics, so try to use the recommended doses and never too much;Â <br/>- For best results in a wash cycle, try not to fill the drum completely, so that the clothes can move freely, allowing for better sanitising and washing.Â </p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_tQfYxe": {
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do Zippy items have a guarantee?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>In the event of a manufacturing defect up to 3 years from the date of purchase, Zippy agrees, in accordance with current legislation, to repair, replace, reduce the price or terminate the contract.<br/>The guarantee must be activated in Zippy's physical shops or via <a href=\"mailto:cliente@zippy.pt\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cliente@zippy.pt </span></a>for online purchases and if it is impossible to visit the physical shop.<br/>Zippy offers an after-sales repair service for most of its nursery articles. Therefore, for incidents related to nursery, the items will be sent to the manufacturer for quality control and repair.<br/>Once the item has been found to be non-compliant, the consumer must inform Zippy within two months.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_LxMzdc": {
          "disabled": false,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do Zippy products undergo quality control?",
            "faq_answer": "<p>Zippy's main objective is to offer safe products. In order to guarantee the highest standards, our controls are meticulous and responsible.<br/>We monitor the entire production process, subjecting our products to various tests to ensure physical, mechanical and chemical safety.<br/>If you have any questions or would like more information about a specific item, you can contact us in the<a href=\"/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Contact\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Customer Support</strong></span></a> section.</p>"
          }
        }
      }
    },
